name: High Für 3 Score
summary: In this game as an arrow-like character you're trapped in a cannabis frenzy. The goal is to dodge all the spirits that come your way. Through the effects box, you can complete the run with unique effects. Along the way, you can also unlock cool stuff to look extra good on the next intoxicating run or compete against different looking spirits. Weekly you have the chance to land on the display with the top 10 best, who have the most achieved high score of that week.
